{"tid":2230903,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"丘品：傳陳德霖組特首競選辦","createTime":"2020-10-05T09:14:26.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-05T11:51:36.000Z","uid":210495,"like":47,"dislike":32,"uniUserReply":66,"replies":[{"pid":"a66abf7776513dc562ad4ad04b560dabfb0f00f8","tid":2230903,"uid":210495,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-05T09:14:26.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/CupidProducer/posts/658377194826327?__cft__[0]=AZVchg9i4FdUq1hg9-C_DqZshj7FrsoOhcYixjD79zIsdDUpheXjXCID5_tNYu9P7e1ScFfA1mEW2bhXizb9AKag_suNEvhPNC2jrtuN-w4ASPkoqK5_S8koC_m5Pgsg7VHs6wJeTQLAPMDcwheFenQnQROibK3Np1E7JwsGxx2PY_c9WDHRrjjFZsWl2Dpv1UA&amp;__tn__=%2CO%2CP-R\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FCupidProducer%2Fposts%2F658377194826327%3F__cft__%5B0%5D%3DAZVchg9i4FdUq1hg9-C_DqZshj7FrsoOhcYixjD79zIsdDUpheXjXCID5_tNYu9P7e1ScFfA1mEW2bhXizb9AKag_suNEvhPNC2jrtuN-w4ASPkoqK5_S8koC_m5Pgsg7VHs6wJeTQLAPMDcwheFenQnQROibK3Np1E7JwsGxx2PY_c9WDHRrjjFZsWl2Dpv1UA%26__tn__%3D%252CO%252CP-R&d=A6Q0GQr%2FGmLii1x5qL7rGD2nqaxvu5zgGSEBmbQkQbg%3D&h=153de85a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/CupidProducer/posts/658377194826327?__cft__[0]=AZVchg9i4FdUq1hg9-C_DqZshj7FrsoOhcYixjD79zIsdDUpheXjXCID5_tNYu9P7e1ScFfA1mEW2bhXizb9AKag_suNEvhPNC2jrtuN-w4ASPkoqK5_S8koC_m5Pgsg7VHs6wJeTQLAPMDcwheFenQnQROibK3Np1E7JwsGxx2PY_c9WDHRrjjFZsWl2Dpv1UA&amp;__tn__=%2CO%2CP-R</a><br />\n<br />\n香港反修例風波未完，緊接迎來下一場政治風波「競選特首」。現任特首林鄭月娥將於2022年6月30日完成任期，有傳林鄭有意競續特首之位，早前於官媒訪問中，表示訂立港區國安法後，重拾「好打得」本色。<br />\n<br />\n除了林鄭，政界近日傳出金管局前總裁陳德霖，著手籌組競選辦公室，並得到金融界及法律界猛人助陣，並於內地連繫一定人脈，增加勝數。而被認為是梁振英的愛將，現任財政司司長陳茂波，亦被指有意爭奪特首。"},{"pid":"4b7a0f827e2d28977ff9d8e578aa09a379ab1af1","tid":2230903,"uid":10757,"like":78,"dislike":3,"score":75,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-10-05T09:16:15.000Z","msg":"陳茂波<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src